42:13.573 --> 42:19.371
<i>♪ Time will save you ♪</i>

42:22.207 --> 42:26.920
<i>♪ You don't need to save yourself ♪</i>

42:28.755 --> 42:34.094
<i>♪ Time will save you ♪</i>

42:37.347 --> 42:42.435
<i>♪ You don't need to save yourself ♪</i>

42:42.561 --> 42:44.771
Hey, over here! We found one!

42:44.896 --> 42:46.398
We got a survivor!

42:46.523 --> 42:48.567
We got a survivor over here!
